<DOCNO> LA042494-0237 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 035399 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 24, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2 
