Diego 2,526 3,394 34.4% $164 $169 2.7% Riverside 1,496 2,279 52.3% $135 $131 
-3.4% San Bernardino 1,551 2,048 32.0% $128 $128 -0.6% Ventura 618 986 59.5% 
$202 $186 -8.0% So. California 14,106 19,557 38.6% $170 $167 -2.0%  
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
