<HEADLINE>
<P>
LEAD-BASED PAINT BROCHURE OFFERED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Dealing With Lead-Based Paint: A Practical Guide for Consumers," a brochure 
outlining a step-by-step approach to managing lead paint and the hazards that 
can be encountered in abatement, has been prepared by the National Paint & 
Coatings Assn. 
</P>
<P>
 A copy of the brochure may be obtained by sending a stamped self-addressed 
envelope to Lead Brochure, Paint and Coatings Industry Information Center, 1500 
Rhode Island Ave., N.W., Washington D.C. 20005. 
</P>
